data.description: Welcome to your spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located on 1.1 acres of fully fenced property in Pleasanton, TX! The home features both a dining room and eat-in kitchen, providing plenty of space to enjoy meals with family and friends. You'll feel relaxed in the spacious master bathroom, complete with a walk-in closet and double vanity. Take in the stunning views from the covered back patio, perfect for relaxing and entertaining. The property includes a shop in the back, waiting for you to make it your own and customize it to your liking. This property offers the ideal combination of space, functionality, and potential. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this property your own and turn it into your dream home! Close to New Methodist South Hospital, Costal Bend College, Pleasanton Municipal Airport.
